  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink405">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>oṇcuṭarp pāṇṭiṟ ceñcuṭar pōla</l>
          <l>maṉaikkuviḷak kāyiṉaṇ maṉṟa kaṉaippeyaṟ</l>
          <l>pūppala vaṇinta vaippiṟ</l>
          <l>puṟavaṇi nāṭaṉ putalvaṉ ṟāyē</l>
        </lg>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          She certainly is a light for the house, just like the red flame in the bright shining lamp
          bowl, the mother of the son of the man from the land with beautiful forests where the
          heavy rains decorate the land with many flowers.
        </p>
      </div>
